out he wasnâ’t.  no one is.  iâ’m stupid for believing someone wanted me.  some one cared for me.  some one loved me.  ha! yeah right,  well i was proven wrong.  again,  and again,  and again.  iâ’m numb,  i canâ’t feel anymore.  no more emotions,  no more pain,  just no more.  i live in a black void,  a void that was caused when my heart was broken for the last time.  iâ’m done! no more! no more pain,  no more hurt,  no more me! no more anything,  i want to feel nothing,  and i want to be nothing.  all i wanted was to feel what love was,  but no iâ’m not allowed.   if i try iâ’ll just end up like i am now.  loveless,  cold,  and lonely.  in my life thereâ’s been heartache,  and pain.  and i donâ’t want to face that pain again.  iâ’m being comforted constantly,  and i wish they would just leave me alone.   iâ’m tired of being cared for,  because no one really cares.  they just act like they do; they act as if oh thatâ’s too bad.  when they donâ’t know anything.  they donâ’t know how i feel.  they never will! what happened to me? i used to be happy,  and now&#x85;nothing.  a blank,  a blank now,  a blank past,  a blank future. 
