st time you can begin to like yourself i think when someone accepts you for the 1st time  you can begin to forgive yourself a little you can begin to face your fears. . .  with courage. . .  ''i have to try my best or i'll become worse and worse even if i cant make up with them even if they all ignore me evev if my heart is still seen as in inferoir i still have to try my best. . . '' i'll try to  and if you get sad again or if things get rough come here for me to keep you company i hope that someday the many tears that were shed will be worth it. . . 
