to be seen once more.  you were picked from a group where all are the same,  yet somehow you are ultimately unique your blinding beauty hits,  and the perfect words canâ’t begin to describe.  more precious than gold,  you are to me.  unforgettable,  etched in memory,  you dazzle me,  day-in,  day-out,  you cease to fail.  you.  you are my rose. 
